Get sdmx dataflows

sdmx_v2_1_get_dataflows.Rd

Get sdmx dataflows from a given endpoint

Usage

sdmx_v2_1_get_dataflows(req = NULL, agencyID = NULL)

Arguments

req

A character string from a given endpoint

agencyID

A character string from a given agencyID

Value

a data.frame with available dataflows

Examples

dfs <- sdmx_v2_1_get_dataflows()
